meta {
  name: Verify an email domain
  type: http
  seq: 6
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/email-domains/{{emailDomainId}}/verify
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Verifies an Email Domain by `emailDomainId`

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `400`: Email domain could not be verified by mail provider
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
